title: 10 photos of Gronk having the best time at the parade
text:
10 photos of Gronk having the best time at the parade Classic Gronk. Post to Facebook 10 photos of Gronk having the best time at the parade Classic Gronk.  //ftw.usatoday.com/2017/02/10-photos-gronk-rob-gronkowski-patriots-super-bowl-51-parade-beer-nfl/   Join the Nation's Conversation   10 photos of Gronk having the best time at the parade Andrew Joseph 4:31 p.m. ET Feb. 7, 2017 3 Shares 
Injury may have kept Rob Gronkowski out of Super Bowl 51, but he was at full GRONK strength for the Patriots' parade on Tuesday. At one point, Gronk caught a beer can, chugged it, then spiked the can . Of course he did. 
But the photos really proved that Gronk had the best time at the parade.
